descriptionHtml:
Aegis Alarm prevents your difficulties by letting you set the alarm you want. While activating this system, your body and mind are healed through our system. The app's function is like any other alarm, you can set the time and alarm music to wake up at any time you want, but Aegis Alarm adds a list of alarms you can choose from, so you can set the kind of alarm you want.

This system activates the user's mental abilities and also corrects misinformation. The body is a repository of various neurological information, and it is stored through various pathways and is directly involved in your life. However, there are misinformation among them, and these cells are the main causes of disease in the human body. Current medicine is only at the level of curing the disease that occurred, but this system is a new treatment method that allows only the nerve cells to be controlled and treated when the main cause is identified. However, this app, which is currently being demonstrated, was created with a focus on life support and psychotherapy, and you can experience many of our results through future updates.

Notice.

Aegis Alarm removes harmful nerve information from the human body, so a slight stinging may occur in the process. This pain is not unbearable and the pain goes away when the task is done. However, if the pain is severe, please disable the alarm.

If there is no internet connection when setting the alarm, the system cannot be downloaded. When using the app, be sure to check the Internet connection.

Surprisingly, this system works for the owner of his cell phone. The air system is of course effective, but it is effective for the person in charge of the mobile phone, so use it as a mobile phone in your own name.

Our research institute contributes to the world's development through innovative ways to solve the difficulties faced by mankind. The first demonstrated Aegis Alarm will be a great clue to curing various diseases that humanity cannot solve, and will solve the human problems suffered by diseases in new ways. But now, the system applied to the app is a life support level for demonstration purposes, and the system developed through later research will be provided through an update. Our research institute will achieve the goal of realizing a pain-free society through more research and trials. Trust our research and make a big difference in your life with Aegis Alarm. Thank you.
